					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You can still get subpixel precision with 16-bit coordinates if you don't need velocity precision lower than 1/16 pixel per frame. This arrangement might even be friendlier to sprite-background collision:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">FEDC BA98 7654 3210<br />|||| |||| |||| ||||<br />|||| |||| |||| ++++- Subpixel<br />|||| ++++-++++------ Whole pixel<br />++++---------------- Map page<br /><br />FEDC BA98 7654 3210<br />|||| |||| |||| ||||<br />|||| |||| ++++-++++- Sub-metatile<br />++++-++++----------- Whole metatile<br /><br /></div></div>

